Name: Basic Aett Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Runestone, Charisma 13 Or Greater
Description: This rune symbolizes the words from a noble's mouth, the speech of a leader, the silvertongue of a merchant. It grants those who channel it greater charm and influence.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACESilvered TongueSPACEAs an action, you speak honeyed words of deception and illusion. Choose a creature you that can hear you within 30 feet of you. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or become charmed by you until the end of your next turn or until you or your companions do anything harmful to it. When this effect ends, the creature is unaware that it was charmed by you.SPACESPACEYou may use this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is deplted. The rune will recharge upon completion of a long rest.
